data.description: Beautiful home in Ridgecrest! Updated galley kitchen/dining overlooks the front yard and features stainless appliances, granite counters, and great storage. Spacious living room features a wood burning fireplace and walkout to the back patio. Master suite features a walk in closet and updated master bath. The other two bedrooms are a great size and share the guest bath. Wood look laminate flooring and neutral paint colors throughout. Large backyard features a covered patio, storage building, and storm cellar. This home is move in ready and ready for YOU! Don't miss your chance to make it yours, schedule your showing today!
